## üòç Features

üì∑ Capture stills, animated gif, collages, ü™É boomerangs and 3d wigglegrams!  
ü´∂ Supports DSLR, Raspberry Pi cameras and webcameras  
üéâ Live preview during countdown and on the home screen  
üõ´ Optimized for speed, highly response UI  
ü´∂ Combine multiple cameras, dedicate one for high quality stills and another one for the livestream  
üí° Integrates with WLED to signal countdown using LED rings  
ü§ù Linux, Raspberry Pi and Windows platforms supported  
üîì Open-source, non-restrictive MIT license  

